(6. SERVICE RESPONSIBILITY MAP) Tj
T*
(-----------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| Layer/Service | Main Responsibility |) Tj
T*
(|---|---|) Tj
T*
(| ChatController | Receives WebSocket STOMP messages and returns bot response |) Tj
T*
(| ChatServiceImpl | Main state machine and orchestration |) Tj
T*
(| SessionService / RedisSessionService | Read/write active user session |) Tj
T*
(| TicketServiceImpl | Create/update tickets and selected ticket items |) Tj
T*
(| OrderServiceImpl | Validate order and parse item selection |) Tj
T*
(| RefundServiceImpl | Calculate deterministic refund from selected ticket items |) Tj
T*
(| DuplicateComplaintServiceImpl | Find previous ticket with same user/order/items/issue |) Tj
T*
(| EscalationServiceImpl | Apply escalation rules |) Tj
T*
(| AIService / OpenAIService | Intent, extraction, normalization, escalation signal |) Tj
T*
(| RuleBasedAIService | Fallback if no API key or API is unavailable |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
